"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526819\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2526819\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dhs1665703261470.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dhs1665703261470.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dhs1665703261470.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dhs1665703261470\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Logical defining the location of JavaScript files for dynamic server pages during\n    development.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"dhs1665703261470__topic_d145433e1_d145434e1_d145435e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dhs1665703261470__p_d145436e1_d145437e1_d145438e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">JAVASCRIPT</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FilePath</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dhs1665703261470__section_thn_ctp_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d92890e65\">Arguments</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FilePath</var>—location of JavaScript files for DSPs during development.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dhs1665703261470__table_w3221ab1b5b3b5_w3222ab1b5b3_w3223ab1b5_w3224ab1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">uniface/webapps/uniface/dspjs</code>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"otb1665703261079.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/otb1665703261079.html\" title=\"The [paths] section of the initialization file specifies the locations of the local working directory, help files, images, and JavaScript files generated during compilation.\">[paths]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dhs1665703261470__section_wcx_jtp_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d92890e116\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">In a default installation, the logical is set to the\n          <span class=\"ph filepath\">uniface/webapps/uniface/dspjs</span> directory of the Uniface installation.\n        This ensures that when you compile a DSP that has <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webtriggers</span> or\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">weboperations</span>, the JavaScript files are generated in the correct\n        location for the web server to find them during testing.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"dhs1665703261470__note_zj1_ltp_xvb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> If you change the default compilation location using\n        the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">JAVASCRIPT</span> setting, you also need to change the default runtime\n        location using the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$JS_BASE_URL</span> assignment setting. Otherwise, the\n        Uniface Server cannot find the generated JavaScript files.</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dhs1665703261470__section_vkt_gyv_cdc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d92890e143\">Example: Changing the Compilation and Runtime Locations of JavaScript Files </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dhs1665703261470__p_d145454e1_d145455e1_d145456e1\">The following settings have been changed to point to a\n        different location for compiled DSP <span class=\"ph filepath\">.js</span> files: <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceInstall</var>/uniface/webapps/uniface/project1/</span>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dhs1665703261470__p_d145457e1_d145458e1_d145459e1\">INI file:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"dhs1665703261470__pre_wt3_ltp_xvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[paths]\njavascript = uniface/webapps/uniface/project1 ; used by compiler</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dhs1665703261470__p_d145460e1_d145461e1_d145462e1\">Assignment file:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"dhs1665703261470__pre_xt3_ltp_xvb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[WEB]\n$JS_BASE_URL = ../project1 ; used at runtime</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mea1665702595617.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$JS_BASE_URL</a><p>Specify the URL where JavaScript files for dynamic server pages are located at runtime.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vkk1665702595354.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Client-Side Triggers and Operations</a><p>Client-side triggers and operations are run in the browser on the client and are implemented in JavaScript. They can be used only in dynamic server pages.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hwb1707717245622.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>webtrigger</a><p>Define a trigger in a DSP that will be executed on the client browser.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gsi1665702594894.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>weboperation…end</a><p>Defines an operation that will be executed on the client browser.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526819\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2526819\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "JAVASCRIPT Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Logical defining the location of JavaScript files for dynamic server pages during development. JAVASCRIPT = FilePath Arguments FilePath —location of JavaScript files for DSPs during development. Default value uniface/webapps/uniface/dspjs File section [paths] Description In a default installation, the logical is set to the uniface/webapps/uniface/dspjs directory of the Uniface installation. This ensures that when you compile a DSP that has webtriggers or weboperations , the JavaScript files are generated in the correct location for the web server to find them during testing. Note: If you change the default compilation location using the JAVASCRIPT setting, you also need to change the default runtime location using the $JS_BASE_URL assignment setting. Otherwise, the Uniface Server cannot find the generated JavaScript files. Example: Changing the Compilation and Runtime Locations of JavaScript Files The following settings have been changed to point to a different location for compiled DSP .js files: UnifaceInstall /uniface/webapps/uniface/project1/ . INI file: [paths] javascript = uniface/webapps/uniface/project1 ; used by compiler Copy Assignment file: [WEB] $JS_BASE_URL = ../project1 ; used at runtime Copy Related Links $JS_BASE_URL Specify the URL where JavaScript files for dynamic server pages are located at runtime. Client-Side Triggers and Operations Client-side triggers and operations are run in the browser on the client and are implemented in JavaScript. They can be used only in dynamic server pages. webtrigger Define a trigger in a DSP that will be executed on the client browser. weboperation…end Defines an operation that will be executed on the client browser. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}